{"tid":937170,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下有冇人傷過手腕韌帶？","createTime":"2018-12-11T10:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T11:51:38.000Z","uid":194580,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"28f9ca4493e5204c3ce85ba6ccb96de34078ef34","tid":937170,"uid":194580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T10:51:01.000Z","msg":"話說兩個月前打波<br />\n有次失重心落地既時候用右手撐咗下<br />\n之後隻手腕就隱隱作痛<br />\n一開始去睇跌打但睇完仲衰過未睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後轉去睇西醫照過X光知道骨冇事<br />\n但兩邊都話好大機會係傷到韌帶<br />\n一路到而家都唔敢打返波住<br />\n想問下有冇人試過咁傷？<br />\n你地係點好返？<br />\n同埋想問下大家有冇好嘅外科醫生介紹？"},{"pid":"d24d42658d2329f18a2315f3dea536be4dae813d","tid":937170,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T10:59:04.000Z","msg":"兩個月前而家先問<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43d8d3d30a6b35343ebe9e4ae3f4366bc09ad4fc","tid":937170,"uid":22708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T11:00:22.000Z","msg":"醫生都會叫你休息"},{"pid":"1d58e43a9ac0030eeccde95f8dca59ad7f64f7b2","tid":937170,"uid":194580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d24d42658d2329f18a2315f3dea536be4dae813d","tid":937170,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T10:59:04.000Z","msg":"兩個月前而家先問<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T11:05:12.000Z","msg":"因為睇完一段時間都冇咩好轉所以想睇下有冇過來人可以講下應該點做"},{"pid":"aef2b5226339825ddece762fb1a9d812d7cbeedb","tid":937170,"uid":194580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43d8d3d30a6b35343ebe9e4ae3f4366bc09ad4fc","tid":937170,"uid":22708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T11:00:22.000Z","msg":"醫生都會叫你休息"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T11:05:50.000Z","msg":"大概要抖幾耐先可以做返運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1889428d76a66e666ca0f339914c104d6aecc6ac","tid":937170,"uid":69977,"like":0,"d